{
  "stem": "4662.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they didn't know-- they didn't, they didn't know they were Jewish in the first place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it changed a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My husband was scared to go in the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a false cupboard made at the back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we heard all the footsteps-- I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we had a big cupboard, crockery cupboard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we made a false door with hooks on the outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we hanged the pots and pans on the hooks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we heard footsteps, or, or the doorbell went and we didn't know who it was, we had to stuff him into the cupboard, in the back.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we put this board with hooks on it, and all the pots and pans, so it was a false back to it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was hidden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The children knew that too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't know-- they thought that was fun.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They thought it was-- I don't know what children think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you talk to my eldest son, he can tell you more about that-- his thoughts-- than I, than I can.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not too often, four or five times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we had a roof.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived on the top floor, and there was a flat roof.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so then my husband could get some color, wouldn't look so white from being inside always.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to have a rope, and he used to climb up the rope onto the roof with my youngest son.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we used to make little pots of food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we used to hand it up to him, the food, [INAUDIBLE] up to him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's how he'd spend some days when it was nice weather to get color in his cheeks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CHUCKLING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the days-- mhm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How long after the war?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
